        "timestamp": "2018-04-17 15:21:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nHi Tomasz, Michal, Skip: Thanks for all the work and input. Please create a separate Jira for the defect fix and submit under a different gerrit. We have had too many changes that have broken run time processing. I would like this separated out in case we have downstream issues. We are too close to Beijing release, so I would like to proceed with caution. I would also like to get more APPC developers looking at this once submit is separated",
